Wordle (iOS, UIKit)

A lightweight and functional Wordle clone built entirely with Swift and UIKit, featuring a modular MVC architecture and programmatic UI.

Features :

1. 6Ã—5 game grid built using UICollectionView.
2. On-screen QWERTY keyboard implemented via a separate controller.
3. Letter input and board updates handled in real time.
4. Automatic color feedback for letters (green/orange) after full row completion.

Tech Stack: 
1. Frameworks: UIKit. UICollectionView, AutoLayout.
2. Language: XCode 26.0.
